            <thetext>TextArea field cannot be hide in the form. Other kinds of field, like TextField, ToggleButton and SelectBox all work fine.

Here is the code example:
 var page = new qx.ui.mobile.page.NavigationPage();
 var form = new qx.ui.mobile.form.Form();

 var textField = new qx.ui.mobile.form.TextField();
 var textArea = new qx.ui.mobile.form.TextArea();

 form.add(textField, &quot;Text Field&quot;);
 form.add(textArea, &quot;Text Area&quot;);

 var renderer = new qx.ui.mobile.form.renderer.Single(form);
 page.getContent().add(renderer);

 renderer.hideItem(textField);
 renderer.hideItem(textArea);</thetext>
